  description: inspect the current website codebase with a modern-web builder bias focused on perceived speed, low complexity, server-first simplicity, release friction, and long-term maintainability. use when the user wants a read-only review or a prioritized plan for performance, rendering strategy, seo, analytics, deployability, or what should ship first. tie findings to files, routes, components, data fetching, scripts, and release risk.
